title: League of Legends Predictive Model
description: Used a dataset on 2024 Esports data to create a website showcasing a report on the impact of void grubs on win rate and player statistics. Showed hypothesis testing and data visualizations of interesting statistics utilizing Plotly.express. The model was made using a Random Forest Classifier utilizing Scikit-Learn and has around an 88.7% accuracy for predicting winrate

title: Video Game Review Genre Classifier
description: Ulitized a Naive Bayes Classifier using Scikit-Learn to classify the genre of a video game based on its review. Created a web app utilizing Streamlit to allow users to try out the trained model. Created for the two day 2025 DataHacks Hackathon

title: Monty Carlo TS AI Bot for StarChess
description: Created a chess AI for a altered version of chess called Starchess. Utilized OpenAI gym and pytorch neural netoworks to create a Monty Carlo Tree Search AI tha competed against other participant's bots. This bot won second place in the 2025 StarChessAI competition.

title: Dino Dash
description: Utilized Pygame to create a twist on the classic chrome dino game. Added updated graphics and sound effects to enhance user experience and added a boss monster at the end of the story mode. Created for the 2025 Tritonware game jam for VGDC
